  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf, \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb0\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd - \u0bb5\u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Nationwide hartal on Thursday after the resignation of the President and Prime Minister - Vasantha Samarasinghe",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "If President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe step down on the 13th tomorrow, we will engage in nationwide hartal action from Thursday.",
        "Vasantha Samarasinghe, head of the united trade union, said that both the heads of state should step down respecting the aspirations of the people of the country.",
        "He said the above while attending a press conference held in Colombo on Monday (11).",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe have no moral right to continue in office.",
        "In the political history of Sri Lanka, no head of state has been so hated by the people. People are very critical of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "The President is looking for an auspicious time to step down when the people of the country are urging him to step down.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe must resign tomorrow. We will go on a massive nationwide hartal from Thursday after the resignation.",
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe should abandon the government maneuver to become the next President once President Gotabaya Rajapaksa steps down.",
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe does not have a Lok Sabha. Respect the aspirations of the people and resign.",
        "If the President and the Prime Minister carry out political maneuvers without resigning, both will face more serious consequences.",
        "He said that until the President formally announced his resignation and communicated the letter to the Speaker and the Speaker made it public to the people, there could be no confidence in the President's resignation."
      ],
